titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on Ethanol, 2,2'-[[4-[(3,5-dinitro-2-thienyl)azo] phenyl]imino]bis-, diacetate (ester).

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary: 10/20/2009--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on Ethanol, 2,2'-YY4-Y(3,5-dinitro-2-thienyl)azo? phenyl?imino?bis-, diacetate (ester).
